DESCRIPTION
This Helper saves the current state of all VMs in the VM mapping and schedule
database after making a Minimega API call to "ns save". The saved information
is written into a backup directory and can optionally be compressed into a
single archive.

**Usage:**  ``firewheel save [--name EXPERIMENT_NAME] [--complete] [--archive]``

Example
+++++++

``firewheel save --name my_experiment --complete --archive``

